                "counteraction": true,
                "damage": {},
                "defense": null,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>You create a visible magical barrier that attempts to counteract teleportation effects and planar travel into or out of the area, including items that allow access to extradimensional spaces. <em>Planar seal</em> tries to counteract any attempt to summon a creature into the area but doesn't stop the creature from departing when the summoning ends.</p>"
