                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within the kerulkagon's reach uses a move action or leaves a square during a move action it's using</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The kerulkagon makes a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If the attack is a critical hit, the action is disrupted.</p>"
